text: Kolokolovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Klenovskoye Selsoviet, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 1 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 3 km south from Klenovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Kolokolovo
